text: József Szalai (18 December 1892 - 29 November 1990) was a Hungarian gymnast. He competed at the 1912 Summer Olympics and the 1928 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1892 births Category:1990 deaths Category:Hungarian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Hungary Category:Gymnasts at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:People from Veszprém County
title: József Szalai (gymnast)
